### Sample API Requests for Automated Academic Process Validator

### Register Users
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123!",
  "role": "admin"
}

###
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Faculty User",
  "email": "faculty@example.com",
  "password": "FacultyPass123!",
  "role": "faculty"
}

###
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Student User",
  "email": "student@example.com",
  "password": "StudentPass123!",
  "role": "student"
}

### Login (example for admin, token used in Authorization header)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123!"
}

### Create Academic Rule (Admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Default Eligibility Rule Set",
  "description": "Standard eligibility for semester exams",
  "attendanceRule": {
    "enabled": true,
    "minPercentage": 75
  },
  "subjectRule": {
    "enabled": true,
    "minMarksPerSubject": 40
  },
  "creditRule": {
    "enabled": true,
    "minTotalCredits": 20
  },
  "prerequisiteRule": {
    "enabled": true,
    "requiredSubjects": ["MATH101", "CS101"]
  },
  "isActive": true
}

### Upsert Student Academic Record (Faculty)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/students
Authorization: Bearer {{FACULTY_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentUserId": "{{STUDENT_USER_ID}}",
  "studentId": "STU-001",
  "attendancePercentage": 80,
  "totalCredits": 22,
  "subjects": [
    {
      "code": "MATH101",
      "name": "Calculus I",
      "marks": 65,
      "credits": 4,
      "completed": true
    },
    {
      "code": "CS101",
      "name": "Introduction to Programming",
      "marks": 72,
      "credits": 4,
      "completed": true
    },
    {
      "code": "ENG101",
      "name": "English",
      "marks": 55,
      "credits": 3,
      "completed": true
    }
  ]
}

### Trigger Validation (Faculty/Admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{FACULTY_OR_ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentUserId": "{{STUDENT_USER_ID}}",
  "ruleId": "{{RULE_ID}}"
}

