### Student View Own Validation Logs
GET http://localhost:5000/api/logs/me
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

### Admin View All Logs
GET http://localhost:5000/api/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

